Kakamega Senator, Cleophas Malala has warned Amani National Congress members of parliament  associating themselves with Deputy President William Ruto. Malala speaking in Lugari constituency, Kakamega county.  He termed the shift of allegiance as disrespect to party leader Musalia Mudavadi. Mudavadi and the DP are locked in succession politics and the battle for Luhya community supremacy. 